metadata.name: EUNOIA
metadata.description:
EUNOIA : Beautiful thinking , a well mind. 

This NFT represents a unique 1/1 photographic artwork shot in the Dolomites Italy. This shot is taken on top of the Sassolungo , A famous mountain of 3181 meters high. 

EUNOIA will be the first of various NFT's within the METANOIA collection.
